content: I do not have subjective preferences or opinions. however, you can choose the hidden gem that best suits your interests and preferences. balboa park is a great option as it offers a wide variety of activities such as museums, gardens, and cultural institutions. la jolla cove is also a popular option for visitors who like to swim, snorkel or enjoy the beach. if you want to explore nature, then torrey pines state natural reserve could be a good choice. ultimately, it depends on what you want to experience and see during your visit to san diego.
